imap jj <ESC>
vmap jj <ESC> 

" Unmap the arrow keys
no <down> ddp
no <left> <Nop>
no <right> <Nop>
no <up> ddkP

ino <down> <Nop>
ino <left> <Nop>
ino <right> <Nop>
ino <up> <Nop>

imap <leader>' ''<ESC>i
imap <leader>" ""<ESC>i
imap <leader>( ()<ESC>i
imap <leader>[ []<ESC>i

"Make the 81st column stand out
highlight ColorColumn ctermbg=magenta
call matchadd('ColorColumn', '\%81v', 100)
